# Travel Planner App

Welcome to the Travel Planner App! This app is designed to assist solo travelers by providing:

- Offline Maps
- Real-time Notifications for Changes/Alternatives
- Community Features for Solo Travelers
- Suggestions for Lesser-Known Destinations Similar to Popular Ones

## Features
- **Offline Maps**: Navigate without an internet connection.
- **Notifications**: Get notified about updates like flight changes, weather, etc.
- **Solo Traveler Community**: Connect with others traveling alone.
- **Destination Suggestions**: Find alternatives to popular destinations.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: ReactJS
- **Backend**: Node.js (if applicable)
- **Maps**: Custom offline map data (Tile-based or vector maps)
- **Notifications**: Push notifications (Firebase or other service)

## Setup

### Prerequisites
Make sure you have Node.js installed on your system.

### Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/travel-planner-app.git

